        "en-US": {
          "description": "AllMiner is a powerful crypto miner optimized specifically for Android devices. It utilizes the original RandomX engine to enable efficient hashing directly on your smartphone's CPU.\n\nFeatures:\n* Native RandomX Engine: Optimized for ARM64 processors.\n* unMineable Support: Mine coins like DOGE, SHIB, SOL, ADA, and many more directly to your wallet.\n* Multi-Threading: Choose the number of CPU cores for maximum performance or minimum heat generation.\n* Hardware Protection: Automatic stop on overheating or low battery (< 20%).\n* Transparent & Open-Source: No hidden fees, full control over your hardware.\n\nNote: Mining on a smartphone can strain the hardware. Use the integrated heat protection for safe operation.",
