          ],
          "summary": "Efficient Android crypto miner with RandomX support.",
          "whatsNew": "Initial release of All Miner!\n- Native RandomX engine integration.\n- unMineable pool support.\n- Multi-thread support with adjustable intensity.\n- Intelligent battery and heat protection.\n- Modern Material 3 design.\n- Added persistent settings: your wallet address, pool URL, and selected coin are now saved automatically.\n- Improved Dashboard: comprehensive overview of mining status, battery level, device temperature, and total hashes.\n- Expanded cryptocurrency support: added many more coins for u"
