        "en-US": {
          "description": "Dualist - Simple, Adaptive, Private.\n\nDualist is a streamlined, high-performance To-Do List application designed for the modern Android ecosystem. It focuses on a seamless transition between mobile and large-screen form factors using a state-of-the-art adaptive architecture.\n\n\ud83c\udf1f KEY FEATURES:\n\n\ud83c\udf13 ADAPTIVE 2-PANE LAYOUT\n- Optimized List-Detail pattern that automatically expands to two panes on tablets and foldables.\n- Providing a high-productivity workspace for large-screen devices.\n\n\ud83c\udfe0 OFFLINE-FIRST & PRIVATE\n- All your tasks are stored locally on your device in a robust Room database.\n- No cloud sync, no data mining, and no accounts required. Your data stays with you.\n\n\ud83d\udeab NO GOOGLE SERVICES REQUIRED\n- Completely free of Google Play Services (GMS).\n- Runs perfectly on de-googled Android distributions and privacy-focused ROMs.\n\n\ud83c\udfa8 VIBRANT MATERIAL 3 DESIGN\n- A bold, energetic color scheme utilizing the latest Material Design 3 principles.\n- Full support for Light and Dark modes.\n- Modern edge-to-edge display integration.\n\n\u2705 CORE TASK MANAGEMENT\n- Effortlessly add, check off, and delete tasks.\n- Intuitive and responsive interface designed for speed and clarity.\n\nDualist is the perfect companion for anyone seeking a fast, private, and beautifully designed task manager that feels at home on any device size. Download Dualist today and experience a new standard in adaptive productivity!\n",
          "featureGraphic": "featureGraphic_QW0NO1znI82Td9V-2QN2thCCM-uqO-lyO7v8ESHlmb8=.png",
